{"tid":1758620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一次選舉光復所有藍絲Page論壇同微博，黑警同政府做事有所顧忌","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T07:26:36.000Z","uid":112551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b389cbf578f03db46670f133df045aaca7b419f3","tid":1758620,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"雖然五大訴求未完全達成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但今次藍絲大敗可以話係輸軍心輸輿論，有藍絲鬧你既時候可以嘲諷一句「沉默大多數呢」，即刻收晒皮。<br />\n唔好話選舉無用，今次選舉提升晒我方軍心，下次任何既行動都可以用「沉默大多數」去打壓黑警同政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW 希望泛民區議員大力加設連儂牆，每日播願榮光歸香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b93e1ca868ca107c81f128f049c2f99a3f7dd3e","tid":1758620,"uid":329453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"直頭用返晒佢地既台詞鬧佢地"}]}